HEADWORD: Murky
<hw>Murk"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Murkier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Murkiest</adjf>.]</amorph> <ety>[OE. <ets>mirke</ets>,
<ets>merke</ets>, AS. <ets>myrce</ets>, <ets>mirce</ets>; akin to Icel.
